results.name: Expansion of Sum_{k>=1} mu(k)*log((theta_3(x^k) + 1)/2)/k, where theta_3() is the Jacobi theta function.
mathematica: nmax = 57; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[MoebiusMu[k] Log[(EllipticTheta[3, 0, x^k] + 1)/2]/k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
nmax = 57; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[MoebiusMu[k] Log[Sum[x^(j^2 k), {j, 0, nmax}]]/k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
